1.skinname: When character's HP is lower than 50%, each attack grants HP equals to 10% DMG.

1.name: Bloodbath Fight
1.skinname: When character's HP is lower than 50%, 20% of taken damage is converted to own HP.

1.name: Sacred Revival

1.name: Thunder Whispering
1.skinname: When attack, there is a 14% chance to render the enemy to increase damage taken by 30% for 5s
